OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalian island offers      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frampant goats up for       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fadoption                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The local mayor of a remote Italian    
OL,6, island overrun with wild goats is      
OL,7, offering to give them away.            
OL,9,FThe idea came to Riccardo Gullo after a
OL,10,Fcensus estimated their population to be
OL,11,Fsix times the human population of 100. 
OL,13,FExperts at navigating the steep        
OL,14,Flandscape of Alicudi, in the Aeolian   
OL,15,Farchipelago north of Sicily, the goats 
OL,16,Fhave become a problem as they damage   
OL,17,Fgardens and allotments.                
OL,19,FApplications to "adopt a goat" must be 
OL,20,Freceived by 10 April.                  
